div.p:
The Kings Maj. hath divided his Army into two parts, the one being nearer to Elſatia, under the command of Monſier de la Force: and the other toward Piccardien; 

under the command of Marſhall de Scomberg, which two Armies, are ſtrengthened with 30000. men. The Marquis de Fiat, is gone towards their Armies, with 40. tun of gold, and ten tun more are ſent to
Italy, to the Duke of Rohan.
